name: 迪伦·比姆
introduction: Dylan Beam was born in Bethesda, MD into a military family. She's lived in Maryland, Texas and, finally, settled in Southern California after her father retired from the US Army. She immediately begged her parents to allow her to audition for TV and Film. Dylan loves meeting new, creative people. She is also a goofball that loves and adores comedy, but also excels in dramatic roles. She is an especially gifted vocalist and has a passion for musical theater where she really comes alive. Dylan also enjoys expressing herself through writing and producing music. When she isn't working she loves spending time with animals, swimming, and quality time with her favorite people.
